Filter-BoxString version 0.05
=============================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Filter::Simple
    Test::More
    Text::Balanced 2.0.0

